# Title: NetNTLM Downgrade Attack
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), wagga
# Date: 2018-03-20
# Level: high
# Description: Detects NetNTLM downgrade attack
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1562.001, attack.t1112
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_net_ntlm_downgrade.yml

EventID=4657 ObjectName="*\\REGISTRY\\MACHINE\\SYSTEM*" ObjectName="*ControlSet*" ObjectName="*\\Control\\Lsa*" ObjectValueName IN ("LmCompatibilityLevel", "NtlmMinClientSec", "RestrictSendingNTLMTraffic")